## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not capture all industry-specific nuances. The perception of job-hopping can vary significantly across different sectors and geographic regions, which may not be fully represented in the sources reviewed. Additionally, the rapidly changing job market means that attitudes towards job-hopping could evolve, necessitating ongoing research to stay current.